WEBVTT

00:00.752 --> 00:04.346
look at your son. lt's your pride
that he sets afire

00:05.123 --> 00:07.353
Two acts to the melodrama!

00:08.093 --> 00:10.687
ln Act One
my daughter and l danced

00:11.696 --> 00:15.291
Act Two
Now you and your son will dance

